00:17:10,180 --> 00:17:11,380
we saw at the airport?

285
00:17:11,579 --> 00:17:12,579
His name is Xu Yao.

286
00:17:14,980 --> 00:17:16,440
Don't you like meat floss?

287
00:17:18,300 --> 00:17:19,430
You like meat floss.

288
00:17:19,740 --> 00:17:21,940
And I'm not picky. So I'll just eat this.

289
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:23,829
You're very observant.

290
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:28,640
His wife is seriously ill.

291
00:17:31,460 --> 00:17:33,260
The local hospital confirmed that

292
00:17:33,260 --> 00:17:35,800
she needs a spinal operation.

293
00:17:36,700 --> 00:17:38,600
It seems to be the back of the neck.

294
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:42,540
But after the surgery,

295
00:17:42,590 --> 00:17:44,390
she will face dreadful sequela.

296
00:17:44,530 --> 00:17:46,080
They dare not do it easily.

297
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:48,440
So they want to go overseas for another check-up.

298
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:49,780
If there is a certain possibility

299
00:17:49,780 --> 00:17:51,300
to diagnosing

300
00:17:51,300 --> 00:17:52,630
another kind of tumour,

301
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:53,900
she won't need surgery,

302
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:54,960
but radiotherapy.

303
00:17:55,300 --> 00:17:56,940
His wife has been sick for many years.

304
00:17:56,940 --> 00:17:58,310
He doesn't have much savings left.

305
00:17:58,310 --> 00:17:59,170
So he came to me.

306
00:17:59,460 --> 00:18:00,790
I saved some for myself.

307
00:18:00,900 --> 00:18:01,860
It's enough for the living expenses

308
00:18:01,860 --> 00:18:02,970
of Qin Xiaonan and me.

309
00:18:02,970 --> 00:18:04,570
I gave him the rest.

310
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:08,560
You're still in debt.

311
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,980
Just leave Qin Xiaonan to me.

312
00:18:10,980 --> 00:18:12,640
He doesn't spend much anyway.

313
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:16,920
No need.

314
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:20,770
Qin Mingyu always pays his living expenses to me.

315
00:18:34,660 --> 00:18:35,660
Xu Yao and his wife

316
00:18:35,660 --> 00:18:37,460
have known each other since childhood.

317
00:18:37,460 --> 00:18:39,520
They've been tangled for many years.

318
00:18:40,630 --> 00:18:43,310
Probably the year before last.

319
00:18:43,610 --> 00:18:44,650
His wife got sick.

320
00:18:45,340 --> 00:18:47,460
And they keep visiting the doctor since then.

321
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:49,700
At that moment, they haven't gotten married yet.

322
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:51,180
His wife refused to get a marriage certificate.

323
00:18:51,180 --> 00:18:52,500
She didn't want to weigh him down.

324
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:53,420
But Xu Yao

325
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:55,270
held a wedding ceremony for her

326
00:18:55,500 --> 00:18:57,160
and insisted on marrying her.

327
00:19:00,060 --> 00:19:01,520
Life is so unpredictable.

328
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:04,010
The previous year, you were still happy with the achievements

329
00:19:04,010 --> 00:19:06,190
but fell into the mud pit the next year.

330
00:19:08,460 --> 00:19:10,700
It's not like Xu Yao could abandon his wife

331
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:12,100
just because she's sick.

332
00:19:12,700 --> 00:19:14,660
And those who have been married.

333
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:15,550
After getting married,

334
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:17,210
if anyone has a career crisis,

335
00:19:18,290 --> 00:19:20,150
they would overcome it together.

336
00:19:22,060 --> 00:19:22,900
Everyone faces ups and downs

337
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:24,340
in their lives.

338
00:19:25,040 --> 00:19:26,640
You can't hope for your lover

339
00:19:26,820 --> 00:19:28,280
to support you selflessly

340
00:19:29,010 --> 00:19:30,810
when you are facing difficulty.

341
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:33,060
but then

342
00:19:33,060 --> 00:19:33,780
you yourself find a better person

343
00:19:33,780 --> 00:19:35,980
when you have achieved a great success.

344
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:37,690
But that's not reality.

345
00:19:38,910 --> 00:19:39,970
It's imagination.

346
00:19:45,970 --> 00:19:47,630
Meng Xiaoshan cares about me.

347
00:19:47,980 --> 00:19:49,970
Don't mind what she said.

348
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,300
Meng Xiaoshan

349
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:54,460
doesn't have a clear understanding of

350
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:55,260
my situation.

351
00:19:56,800 --> 00:19:58,130
At most, only two years.

352
00:19:58,540 --> 00:19:59,740
I will settle my debt.

353
00:20:05,770 --> 00:20:07,630
Then I'll save money to marry you.

354
00:20:21,490 --> 00:20:22,170
You wish!

355
00:20:24,860 --> 00:20:26,590
Are you not willing to marry me?

356
00:20:28,270 --> 00:20:29,000
If you agree,

357
00:20:30,070 --> 00:20:32,060
we'll sleep in the same room tonight.

358
00:20:32,060 --> 00:20:34,520
If you don't agree, we'll sleep separately.

359
00:20:35,860 --> 00:20:38,110
The room we booked yesterday

360
00:20:40,580 --> 00:20:41,590
has a double bed.

361
00:21:04,890 --> 00:21:11,150
[Jimu Cliff]

362
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:14,690
Captain Lu.

363
00:21:17,610 --> 00:21:19,470
How have you been these two years?

364
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:20,400
Good.

365
00:21:22,120 --> 00:21:22,740
This is...

366
00:21:24,130 --> 00:21:25,940
Gui Xiao, my girlfriend.

367
00:21:26,860 --> 00:21:27,260
Hello.

368
00:21:27,840 --> 00:21:29,390
Hello, I'm Sun Hao.

369
00:21:31,370 --> 00:21:32,030
Captain Lu.

370
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,490
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

371
00:21:33,490 --> 00:21:34,020
If you told me earlier,

372
00:21:34,020 --> 00:21:34,620
I would have arranged for a deluxe couple package

373
00:21:34,620 --> 00:21:35,290
for you.

374
00:21:37,130 --> 00:21:38,700
Do you still have this kind of service?

375
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:39,680
It's for vacation.

376
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:41,740
Of course we have suites for couples.

377
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:45,900
Why are you taking me here?

378
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:46,980
It's cold.

379
00:21:46,980 --> 00:21:47,660
Hang in there.

380
00:21:47,660 --> 00:21:48,860
The sunrise will be beautiful tomorrow morning.

381
00:21:48,860 --> 00:21:49,390
Trust me.

382
00:21:54,270 --> 00:21:55,000
Let me do it.

383
00:21:56,830 --> 00:21:58,290
You came at the right time.

384
00:21:58,620 --> 00:21:59,980
Winter is not the peak season.

385
00:21:59,980 --> 00:22:01,560
There are fewer people staying here.

386
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:02,130
Look,

387
00:22:02,660 --> 00:22:03,140
during the summer,

388
00:22:03,140 --> 00:22:04,540
it is an endless prairie.

389
00:22:04,580 --> 00:22:05,060
We simply followed

390
00:22:05,060 --> 00:22:05,960
the design of a Mongolian yurt

391
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:07,020
and built a resort.

392
00:22:12,950 --> 00:22:13,550
Thank you.

393
00:22:16,610 --> 00:22:16,940
Xiao.

394
00:22:17,660 --> 00:22:18,420
Actually, I'm not

395
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:19,620
in Captain Lu's team.

396
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:21,090
I'm not qualified.

397
00:22:21,220 --> 00:22:21,970
They are

398
00:22:22,100 --> 00:22:23,250
all elites.

399
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:25,820
But Captain Lu taught us how to dismantle bombs.

400
00:22:25,820 --> 00:22:26,680
He's my master.

401
00:22:27,140 --> 00:22:28,460
Do you know how I felt

402
00:22:28,460 --> 00:22:29,990
when I first met Captain Lu?

403
00:22:30,090 --> 00:22:31,390
He's so arrogant.

404
00:22:31,870 --> 00:22:33,130
The first time I saw him

405
00:22:33,130 --> 00:22:34,060
standing there,

406
00:22:34,070 --> 00:22:35,540
the first sentence he said was,

407
00:22:35,540 --> 00:22:37,070
"It's not easy to be a SWAT."

408
00:22:37,980 --> 00:22:39,250
He scared us on the first day

409
00:22:39,250 --> 00:22:41,540
saying that there is no absolute expert in dismantling bombs.

410
00:22:41,540 --> 00:22:43,670
Everyone is just risking their lives.

411
00:22:44,700 --> 00:22:45,110
Well,

412
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:46,580
the EOD expert,

413
00:22:46,580 --> 00:22:48,200
who had a communication with him last year,

414
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:49,930
was just killed in the war zone.

415
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:52,110
When I first learned it,

416
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:53,260
I was very careful.

417
00:22:53,470 --> 00:22:55,000
I thought I was successful.

418
00:22:55,500 --> 00:22:56,420
So I cut it off.

419
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:57,730
And then he came.

420
00:22:58,460 --> 00:23:00,190
Do you know what Captain Lu said?

421
00:23:00,190 --> 00:23:00,620
What?

422
00:23:01,050 --> 00:23:03,050
He said I was already blown to death.

423
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:06,580
Before Captain Lu left...

424
00:23:06,580 --> 00:23:07,110
Alright.

425
00:23:07,870 --> 00:23:09,530
Let's not talk about the past.

426
00:23:09,570 --> 00:23:10,650
How can I not?

427
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:12,210
That was all your heroic deeds.

428
00:23:12,210 --> 00:23:12,600
Xiao.

429
00:23:12,950 --> 00:23:13,810
When Captain Lu

430
00:23:14,020 --> 00:23:14,940
covered for others,

431
00:23:14,940 --> 00:23:15,600
he was shot.

432
00:23:21,200 --> 00:23:22,860
You should have seen the scar.

433
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:45,340
Captain Lu.

434
00:23:46,570 --> 00:23:48,170
The third one from this side.

435
00:23:48,340 --> 00:23:50,140
I have to help my mom with the account.

436
00:23:50,140 --> 00:23:50,800
Captain Lu.

437
00:23:51,070 --> 00:23:52,140
The horses are all here.

438
00:23:52,140 --> 00:23:53,270
Pick one if you want.

439
00:23:54,530 --> 00:23:55,590
I'll go back first.

440
00:24:12,620 --> 00:24:13,460
It's all dark.

441
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:15,420
They slept so early.

442
00:24:15,780 --> 00:24:16,390
It's late.

443
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:18,520
It's already eleven.

444
00:24:37,610 --> 00:24:39,440
How many beds are in there?

445
00:25:03,750 --> 00:25:08,480
