00:25:17,360 --> 00:25:22,440
♫Your shadow becomes further with the long road♫

448
00:25:23,310 --> 00:25:27,580
♫It becomes the truth of my empty dream♫

449
00:25:30,750 --> 00:25:35,960
♫Love is the gentle looks of a youth♫

450
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:42,650
♫Be bolder, come closer♫

451
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:49,530
♫You are the curtain call speech for my youth♫

452
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:54,960
♫You are everything on my tiny planet♫

453
00:25:57,120 --> 00:25:59,640
♫I've thought about it once in a while♫

454
00:25:59,260 --> 00:25:59,820
May I?

455
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:02,170
♫The wind blows towards the snowfield♫

456
00:26:03,820 --> 00:26:09,420
♫Your light will drive away all the cold nights♫

457
00:26:05,630 --> 00:26:06,890
You kissed me that time

458
00:26:07,270 --> 00:26:08,200
without asking.

459
00:26:11,380 --> 00:26:12,990
♫I'm willing to♫

460
00:26:13,120 --> 00:26:16,390
♫Hold all my thoughts♫

461
00:26:16,860 --> 00:26:22,780
♫All dreams are coming for you♫

462
00:26:26,820 --> 00:26:28,620
It was normal when I was injured.

463
00:26:30,090 --> 00:26:31,750
Aren't you an EOD technician?

464
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:33,630
EOD is my major.

465
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:36,370
The duty of SWAT

466
00:26:36,740 --> 00:26:39,170
is to maintain the stability of our country.

467
00:26:39,170 --> 00:26:40,530
Whether it's a gunfight, knife battle,

468
00:26:40,530 --> 00:26:42,390
or bomb, I've encountered it all.

469
00:26:43,330 --> 00:26:44,990
You didn't mention it before.

470
00:26:47,780 --> 00:26:48,910
What's there to say?

471
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,080
On the first day I went in,

472
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:53,760
the old captain told me

473
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:55,920
there were things

474
00:26:56,850 --> 00:26:58,580
you shouldn't tell your family

475
00:26:58,660 --> 00:26:59,860
and you'd better not.

476
00:27:00,780 --> 00:27:01,780
It has no benefits

477
00:27:03,690 --> 00:27:04,890
except to worry them.

478
00:27:13,100 --> 00:27:14,630
All these years in the SWAT,

479
00:27:15,310 --> 00:27:16,710
none of us was uninjured.

480
00:27:18,700 --> 00:27:19,220
Last year,

481
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:20,080
a new kid

482
00:27:20,620 --> 00:27:22,280
hurt his leg during training.

483
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,980
He was quite happy.

484
00:27:25,260 --> 00:27:25,750
He said,

485
00:27:26,780 --> 00:27:28,110
finally, he was injured

486
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,630
and dared to say

487
00:27:30,090 --> 00:27:31,950
that he belonged to the squadron.

488
00:27:55,550 --> 00:27:56,840
You insisted on going.

489
00:27:59,190 --> 00:28:01,250
You didn't listen to any of my advice.

490
00:28:02,940 --> 00:28:04,540
Now you've suffered so much.

491
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:11,700
This is crazy.

492
00:28:12,210 --> 00:28:14,660
Why do you have to come to the prairie in winter?

493
00:28:14,660 --> 00:28:16,070
People usually come in summer.

494
00:28:16,070 --> 00:28:16,650
It's freezing all night.

495
00:28:16,650 --> 00:28:17,780
I am frozen to death.

496
00:28:18,130 --> 00:28:19,330
The craziest thing is

497
00:28:19,540 --> 00:28:20,800
watching the sunrise.

498
00:28:20,820 --> 00:28:22,060
Sunrise my ass.

499
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:49,130
I'm going to sleep with Sun Hao.

500
00:29:03,150 --> 00:29:04,070
Calm down.

501
00:29:05,230 --> 00:29:06,260
We've been frozen all night.

502
00:29:06,260 --> 00:29:07,280
Why are you still watching the sunrise?

503
00:29:07,280 --> 00:29:07,940
Okay, go on.

504
00:29:09,740 --> 00:29:10,580
All right.

505
00:29:10,970 --> 00:29:12,100
It's all your fault.

506
00:29:20,570 --> 00:29:22,970
Did you just quarrel with your girlfriend?

507
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:25,040
Besides this,

508
00:29:25,450 --> 00:29:27,180
I can't think of anything else.

509
00:29:27,250 --> 00:29:27,700
Your girlfriend is still

510
00:29:27,700 --> 00:29:28,900
lying on her warm bed.

511
00:29:29,140 --> 00:29:29,970
What can you do coming out

512
00:29:29,970 --> 00:29:31,430
in the middle of the night?

513
00:29:46,640 --> 00:29:48,170
Go that way. It's spacious.

514
00:29:51,830 --> 00:29:52,590
Wait for me.

515
00:30:09,360 --> 00:30:10,890
Last time when we came here,

516
00:30:11,140 --> 00:30:12,470
his wife was still here.

517
00:30:13,290 --> 00:30:14,330
Now, she's gone.

518
00:30:14,590 --> 00:30:15,630
He's left alone.

519
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:19,820
Let me knock on the door.

520
00:30:19,820 --> 00:30:21,100
He has said it many times.

521
00:30:21,100 --> 00:30:21,880
When you return,

522
00:30:21,880 --> 00:30:23,680
he wants to have a drink with you.

523
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:25,720
It's too late.

524
00:30:27,670 --> 00:30:28,870
The light is still on.

525
00:30:29,780 --> 00:30:31,330
The guest-welcoming light is on.

526
00:30:31,330 --> 00:30:33,530
It means that the host hasn't slept yet.

527
00:30:41,030 --> 00:30:41,560
Who is it?

528
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:45,460
Good evening.

529
00:30:47,860 --> 00:30:49,120
Why are you here today?

530
00:30:55,780 --> 00:30:56,440
Captain Lu.

531
00:31:00,630 --> 00:31:01,940
Come on.

532
00:31:02,180 --> 00:31:02,980
Here, take it.

533
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:04,520
Here, take it.

534
00:31:05,180 --> 00:31:05,850
Sit down.

535
00:31:08,540 --> 00:31:09,630
I made it myself.

536
00:31:10,790 --> 00:31:12,320
Have a taste.

537
00:31:19,920 --> 00:31:20,490
Come on.

538
00:31:20,490 --> 00:31:21,160
Drink.

539
00:31:21,250 --> 00:31:21,650
Drink.

540
00:31:29,840 --> 00:31:31,300
The last time we met was...

541
00:31:31,820 --> 00:31:32,620
Two years ago.

542
00:31:33,100 --> 00:31:33,970
Yes.

543
00:31:35,070 --> 00:31:36,730
Is Captain Lu still in Qining?

544
00:31:38,260 --> 00:31:39,700
I went back to my hometown.

545
00:31:39,700 --> 00:31:40,700
Back to hometown?

546
00:31:43,260 --> 00:31:44,020
Okay.

547
00:31:45,570 --> 00:31:46,900
You've reached the age.

548
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:48,900
It's good to be with your parents.

549
00:31:51,060 --> 00:31:51,390
Here.

550
00:31:53,530 --> 00:31:54,130
Let's eat.

551
00:31:58,860 --> 00:32:00,320
You're drinking too fast.

552
00:32:01,850 --> 00:32:02,180
Here.

553
00:32:21,050 --> 00:32:21,710
Captain Lu.

554
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:23,210
Here.

555
00:32:26,420 --> 00:32:28,690
I wish you could stay for a few more days.

556
00:32:29,740 --> 00:32:31,470
My youngest son is coming back.

557
00:32:32,580 --> 00:32:33,180
Next time.

558
00:32:33,940 --> 00:32:35,310
When he goes to Beijing next time,

559
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:36,380
ask him to come to me.

560
00:32:36,380 --> 00:32:36,900
Okay.

561
00:32:44,940 --> 00:32:46,140
Actually, when I heard about

562
00:32:46,140 --> 00:32:47,650
your family situation at first,

563
00:32:47,650 --> 00:32:48,780
I was quite shocked.

564
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:50,820
What for?

565
00:32:51,570 --> 00:32:54,100
There are over 20 police officers in a family.

566
00:32:56,380 --> 00:32:57,500
It is heroic to say,

567
00:32:58,230 --> 00:32:59,360
but difficult to do.

568
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:03,040
Outsiders don't understand.

569
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:04,570
We, as your peers, know that

570
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:06,880
the family glory

571
00:33:08,690 --> 00:33:10,490
